<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我叫沙拉查，是波斯王的妻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我并不是国王的第一任妻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哎，他曾经有过上百个妻子！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会慢慢解释的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几年来，国王每天都会和一名美丽的女子结婚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然而在第二天早上，他会下令把妻子杀死！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50282</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都对此感到非常气愤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50283</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56873</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>父母们失声痛哭，所有的年轻女孩儿都活在恐惧之中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56873</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有人想和国王结婚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是国王可以做任何他想做的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于有一天轮到了我，我成为了国王的新娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是你们可以看到，我还活着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在我们结婚的那天晚上，我亲吻了一下国王，说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“陛下，我给你讲个故事来打发时间，怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我最喜欢听故事了！”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，我给他讲了一个充满冒险经历的精彩的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王听了一个晚上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当我讲完故事时，国王拍手说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，这个故事真是太精彩了！你再给我讲一个吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在那时，阳光照进了窗户，公鸡开始啼叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，”我说，“夜晚已经过去了，没有时间了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果您让我活着，今晚我会为您讲一个更精彩的故事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142538</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以那天，国王没有杀我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到了晚上，我给他讲了一个非常长的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>直到早上，我的故事还没有结束。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162348</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，为了听故事的结尾，国王再一次让我活了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就这样一天接着一天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天早上，国王为了可以听到更多的精彩故事，就让我多活一天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们想听一听国王最喜欢的故事之一吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果想听的话，就让我为你们讲述阿拉丁和神灯的故事吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很久很久以前，一个穷裁缝住在一个临着大海的遥远的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>裁缝有一个儿子，叫阿拉丁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁除了玩儿，不愿意做任何事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁十岁的时候，裁缝说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“儿子，你必须学会一样本领。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我来教你，你就可以和我一样成为一名裁缝了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221482</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我才不要工作呢。”阿拉丁抱怨道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每次裁缝转过身，阿拉丁就跑出门去玩儿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“回来！”裁缝大声叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是阿拉丁就是不听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁的父亲非常伤心，于是他病了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他就因伤心过度而去世了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁和他的母亲相依为命。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为了买面包，我没日没夜地纺纱。”阿拉丁的妈妈叹息道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁的妈妈名叫泽巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她说：“你一天到晚就知道玩儿。只有饿的时候才会回家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就这样，不知不觉阿拉丁已经十七岁了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那一年，一个名叫马格里布的陌生人来到了这座城市。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有人知道马格里布其实是一名魔法师，因为这是他的秘密。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，马格里布看着在街上玩耍的孩子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他灰白的眼睛在满是灰尘的长袍头巾下闪亮起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他指着阿拉丁，向身边的一个小孩儿问道：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个男孩儿是谁？他的父亲是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是阿拉丁。”小孩儿说，“他是裁缝的儿子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布问了很多问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他了解了关于阿拉丁的所有事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>349175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“寻找结束了！”马格里布说，“我找到他了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>